oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Gray Printing Company Envelope with Notes
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Gray Printing Company; Offset printing;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color (blue on white) envelope with the Gray Printing Company name and address printed in the top left corner. It was probably printed on the offset press. Some handwritten notes are found on the envelope, including a possible poster design and poster copy.
